{"tid":2329591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★11月失業綜援個案達1.9萬宗　按年急增54%","createTime":"2020-12-17T10:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T10:48:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d3e5836ff2c291da1133c870282c7fc648cae947","tid":2329591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:22:03.000Z","msg":"本港最新失業率高企6.3%，因失業而領取綜援的個案升至1.9萬宗，按年大增54%！社會福利署表示，因失業而領取綜援的個案持續上升，11月的申請個案較上月增加了8.3%，至931宗，較去年同月亦上升約52.4%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201217/bkn-20201217170805872-1217_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201217%2Fbkn-20201217170805872-1217_00822_001.html&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28c0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=aaa4fbfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201217/bkn-20201217170805872-1217_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"db108c0f1b3e03f133c3336602fda801978a47f8","tid":2329591,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53f5d35373a214877b2b1562f61a08c77e0b41a","tid":2329591,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:25:17.000Z","msg":"越來越多人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18452ba6339f67d8180d3ce0c1baa9412e51620","tid":2329591,"uid":215755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"依家多左bno太空人計劃<br />\n人唔係香港都食都老綜"},{"pid":"235068087363681c30bd198eea5f6e4b2d8acc1f","tid":2329591,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:36:44.000Z